wiki.summary: “Born 2 Be Great” served as a promotional single for New York rapper Lil Tjay’s sophomore album, Destined 2 Win. On the track, Tjay reminisces about his troubled childhood, in which he and his friends went through trouble to get where he is today. He touches on his focuses today and how he aims to be the greatest of all time. Read more on Last.fm.
